{"tid":1907233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂潮牌新衫出現五一手勢 官網直認「外國勢力」創作","createTime":"2020-03-02T12:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T19:28:16.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d86430af3553953f7a510b415496e4af4b7c66a","tid":1907233,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ar13s2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ar13s2.jpg&h=d38a6573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「五大訴求 缺一不可」，這口號香港人呼喊了大半年，加上五一手勢亦相當形象化深入民心。過去半年，藝人有任何風吹草動皆有可能跟反送中運動扯上關係，都會被大陸小粉紅狙擊，惟自武漢肺炎爆發後，中國輿論焦點轉風向，少有提及香港。不過大陸昨日實施最嚴格的網上言論規範，明顯針對大陸網民公開要求言論自由，想不到最嚴網規範公佈後翌日，微博再將矛頭轉向香港反送中運動，似乎想轉移視線。<br />\n<br />\n今次受害者是余文樂，他所建立的時裝品牌MADNESS官方微博今日為宣傳網店開張而推出多款新衫，其中一款長袖衞衣背後有一雙手圖案，分別舉起5隻手指及1隻手指，微博網民紛紛指「余文樂不忘初心」、「幫廢青宣傳」、「表面愛國，內裏支持港獨」等，亦有人開始剪MADNESS舊衫割席。<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅出擊後，該MADNESS宣傳貼文已被刪走，兼出文澄清被惡意抹黑，又指圖案「出自美國著名插畫師之手筆」，而該五一手勢的意思則是「概念單純代表著余文樂『No.6/6六叔』之稱號。」在一片愛國心之下，MADNESS正式講明圖案出自「外國勢力」之手，未知會否引來更多攻勢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200302/NHT7M4GKENLWDD5J5COPA5HQ4U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200302%2FNHT7M4GKENLWDD5J5COPA5HQ4U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=849a1c93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200302%2FNHT7M4GKENLWDD5J5COPA5HQ4U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5eff3e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200302/NHT7M4GKENLWDD5J5COPA5HQ4U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5fc1dee695664a4604b5c47fae27be4d0f41c8c7","tid":1907233,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"人一乃 腦便柒"},{"pid":"a799969f09636a76b27a9e5ffb192574ab3a4596","tid":1907233,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fc1dee695664a4604b5c47fae27be4d0f41c8c7","tid":1907233,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"人一乃 腦便柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"1d751e68af9a30b8673353fcc3d48f913dc48c53","tid":1907233,"uid":196329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KvrJzxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKvrJzxo.jpg&h=1e634316&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}